Examples<br>
Focus items, I LOVE the idea, several people have said this, I think it would be the single BEST addition to the everquest game.  They're not gonna do it tho, they said they would with luclin, didn't have time and didn't, maybe hope next expansion they will, but dont expect it this time<br>
<br>
Better summons, I really dont give a @#%$ if I can make a loaf of bread or a 15/20 weapon, it doesn't effect me at all.  Stop asking for them, again they need lotsa work but verant has stated time and again that they do not want our stuff so powerful that it has an impact on the economy, and people would twink with a mage friend giving them a weapon and/or armor when they log on, instead of buying it.  Stuff with effects on it?  same thing, not gonna happen.  I would LOVE more summons, but lets face it, we didn't start a mage so we could conjure up weapons, we started it for the pets, with the combination of having potent nukes, and the other aspects.<br>
